{"tid":2397528,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Galaxy S21 Ultra 月球照驗證，外媒：證實沒有造假","createTime":"2021-02-06T13:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T05:31:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e1fe28a0e177b34794c3e7154dd6ba2a2aebf4","tid":2397528,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"三星全新 Galaxy S21 旗艦手機系列的 Galaxy S21 Ultra 手機內建 1.08 億畫素相機的 4 鏡頭攝影系統，使用 3 倍與 10 倍光學變焦的遠鏡頭，配合 Zoom Lock 功能可拍攝遠處物體的清晰圖像，官方聲稱連拍攝月球也沒有問題。近日有網友質疑，更懷疑三星宣傳照造假，不過有專家多方驗證後，推論手機拍出來的照片不像造假，更比使用數位相機與高價鏡頭拍的相片更清晰細緻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/03152128/did-you-know-samsungs-galaxy-camera-app-now-has-a-moon-mode-624x291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F03152128%2Fdid-you-know-samsungs-galaxy-camera-app-now-has-a-moon-mode-624x291.jpg&h=8c1baf2d&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n<br />\nGalaxy S21 Ultra 宣傳手機的拍攝功能時，指利用 100x Zoom 可輕鬆拍攝月球，但有網友試用時發現，拍得的月球照並不如三星展示清晰銳利，開始質疑三星是否如中國其他品牌，利用 AI 技術造假。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/02/03/moon/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F02%2F03%2Fmoon%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIV95pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=5632e329\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/02/03/moon/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"ee7db7879768e607f3103fd1eb845b231f4a2894","tid":2397528,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T13:30:09.000Z","msg":"外媒《InputMag》其後聯繫相關技術專家，以證實 Samsung 有否造假。有專家指 Samsung 官方給出的月球照的確有偽造的可能性，並指照片在光學上超出現實，有可能是內建了添加月球頂部紋理的功能，故實試利用 100x Zoom 拍攝一瓣大蒜以及高爾夫球，但發現手機沒有通過添加紋理將這些物體變成月亮，而翻查相機 APK 後也沒有任何發現。"},{"pid":"9a349f7ec692e27f4a4c3aca2b1842a0a3cea58a","tid":2397528,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"《InputMag》其後決定直接比較 Galaxy S21 Ultra 和裝上 200-600mm 焦距鏡頭 Sony A7R III 所拍攝的月球圖片，排列了兩者拍出的圖像線條和紋理，發現照片特徵完全符合，證實 Galaxy S21 Ultra 的確有拍攝月球的能力。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/943288747823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F943288747823.jpg&h=e28b301d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">▲Galaxy S21 Ultra 100x Zoom<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/23789489237894378923.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F23789489237894378923.jpg&h=cf696f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Sony A7R III 600mm</span></p><br />\n<br />\n不過，成像顯然未有官方提供的照片清晰，故記者利用 Adobe Lightroom 中對其進行了銳化處理，發現 Galaxy S21 Ultra 的圖像有因而變好，甚至比起 Sony 的無反光鏡相機拍得更好。事實證明，Samsung 並沒有偽造月球照片，只是有可能利用後製軟件處理圖像，故推翻了造假的說法。"},{"pid":"bc66ae21454640eed736a6730bc84c353eec683a","tid":2397528,"uid":72395,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"相機嗰張好明顯無對到焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e951ddabb6a35acd38228bd2e7b56581dc6cf6","tid":2397528,"uid":66365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"似sony 造假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ba55f6b7110076a99b3b5d5f34e8a00857d0e7","tid":2397528,"uid":226155,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"三星無造假=新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcea467937e2d56e998a6cd34b6688aab8de054","tid":2397528,"uid":242330,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1SmFeA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1SmFeA.jpg&h=7d55c393&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我最遠得105mm，600mm會咁濛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876a6f9227c9209ede336c85147426fdd04b5866","tid":2397528,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T02:05:05.000Z","msg":"600mm 個張無落腳？"},{"pid":"eb134402df72800379ae5940258d1ef06c7bc3ae","tid":2397528,"uid":31990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T20:49:21.000Z","msg":"即刻收晒支那皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6932fddbe7d65da860cc51b525c2b7f2d36e6e3","tid":2397528,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T17:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892ee1dd7aaf7adbb3949baf5bbf4ac789f751ca","tid":2397528,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymZtFZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymZtFZ8.png&h=9f822d38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYZQUj9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYZQUj9.png&h=f86aed9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nzt99Tu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnzt99Tu.png&h=c44d95a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKP9qrR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKP9qrR.png&h=c598ad51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k3iuqrS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk3iuqrS.png&h=778cd01b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XyLXzke.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyLXzke.png&h=51527de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />